title: The Top 10 NFL Mock Draft and Little-Known Free Agency Facts | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
We run through the first 10 picks of the NFL draft, predicting who each team will select (0:25), before former NFL agent Joel Corry calls in to explain what’s happening in free agency, including how the CBA is affecting players' new contracts, how quarterback supply exceeded demand, and how this year was different from previous years (33:50).
Host: Kevin Clark
Guest: Danny Kelly and Joel Corry
